      <title>特朗普的盟友和儿媳在共和党全国委员会中担任前两名</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/trump-ally-daughter-in-law-snag-top-two-posts-at-rnc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的亲密盟友被任命为共和党全国委员会的两个最高职位，此前前任主席因对筹款活动以及与前总统 2024 年总统竞选活动的协调不满而辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/trump-ally-daughter-in-law-snag-top-two-posts-at-rnc</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 17:10:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>公共部门招聘正在推动加拿大劳动力市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/public-sector-hiring-is-driving-the-labor-market-in-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[公共部门的就业增长足以抵消上个月加拿大企业的损失，凸显了政府招聘支撑的劳动力市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/public-sector-hiring-is-driving-the-labor-market-in-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 17:00:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度与英国贸易谈判即将结束，但关键问题尚未解决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/india-uk-free-trade-talks-set-to-end-with-no-breakthrough-on-major-issues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，英国和印度之间的最新一轮贸易谈判似乎将在重大悬而未决的问题上取得突破的情况下结束，这意味着在印度举行大选之前不太可能达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/india-uk-free-trade-talks-set-to-end-with-no-breakthrough-on-major-issues</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 16:45:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着 2024 年大选的临近，摇摆州居民的痛苦指数最高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/swing-state-residents-lead-misery-index-as-2024-election-ignites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最有可能决定2024年总统选举的七个摇摆州比美国其他地区面临着更多的经济困境，这为乔·拜登总统的连任竞选增添了障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/swing-state-residents-lead-misery-index-as-2024-election-ignites</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 16:39:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登通过摇摆州旅行闪电战向特朗普发起攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/biden-turns-up-heat-on-trump-with-swing-state-travel-blitz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的竞选团队希望抓住他国情咨文演讲的势头，发起一场旅行闪电战，旨在吸引选民对他即将与唐纳德·特朗普复赛的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/biden-turns-up-heat-on-trump-with-swing-state-travel-blitz</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普安排 9160 万美元保证金以上诉卡罗尔判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/trump-seeks-court-approval-of-91-6-million-bond-over-carroll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 在上诉期间获得了 9160 万美元的保证金，以推迟支付 E·让·卡罗尔 (E. Jean Carroll) 诽谤案的判决结果，从而平息了有关他能否在现金紧缩的情况下筹集到这笔资金的疑问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/trump-seeks-court-approval-of-91-6-million-bond-over-carroll</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 15:47:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度反对党任命第一批选举候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/india-s-opposition-party-names-first-set-of-election-candidates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度主要反对党印度国大党的高级领导人拉胡尔·甘地将在印度南部喀拉拉邦的现任席位上参加即将举行的全国选举，该党公布了一些参加竞选的候选人名单。民意调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/india-s-opposition-party-names-first-set-of-election-candidates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 15:19:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麻省理工学院因反犹太主义而陷入众议院委员会调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/mit-dragged-into-house-committee-investigation-over-antisemitism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以色列后，众议院教育和劳动力委员会将麻省理工学院列入其正在调查校园反犹太主义的大学名单中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/mit-dragged-into-house-committee-investigation-over-antisemitism</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 14:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚考虑在骚乱后放弃对索马里兰的承认</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/ethiopia-may-scrap-somaliland-recognition-amid-regional-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，埃塞俄比亚正在考虑废除一项承认索马里兰脱离国家的计划，因为国际社会压力很大，要求缓和该提议带来的地区紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/ethiopia-may-scrap-somaliland-recognition-amid-regional-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 11:00:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>核监管机构要求俄罗斯结束对乌克兰核电站的占领</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/nuclear-watchdog-demands-russia-end-occupation-of-ukraine-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国原子能监管机构重申，由于担心安全状况恶化可能导致核电站崩溃，因此再次要求俄罗斯将欧洲最大核电站交还给乌克兰控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/nuclear-watchdog-demands-russia-end-occupation-of-ukraine-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 07:21:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
